sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Felhasználó
    participant FE as Frontend<br/>(ReservationModal)
    participant H as useReservations<br/>hook
    participant Q as TanStack Query
    participant API as Express<br/>POST /api/reservations
    participant Z as Zod<br/>validáció
    participant Auth as JWT<br/>middleware
    participant DB as SQLite<br/>adatbázis

    U->>FE: Kiválasztja a központot<br/>és az időslot-ot
    FE->>FE: Form validáció<br/>(slot a jövőben?)
    FE->>H: createReservation({ centerId, slotStart, slotEnd })
    H->>Q: mutation
    Q->>API: POST /api/reservations<br/>+ Authorization: Bearer <jwt>
    API->>Auth: requireAuth(req)
    Auth-->>API: req.user = { sub, email, role }
    API->>Z: parseAsync(req.body)
    Z-->>API: { centerId, slotStart, slotEnd }
    API->>API: slot múlt-ellenőrzés
    API->>DB: SELECT shopping_centers WHERE id=?
    DB-->>API: { capacity, occupied, name }
    API->>API: kapacitás check<br/>(occupied < capacity?)
    API->>DB: SELECT FROM reservations<br/>WHERE user_id=? AND slot_start=?
    DB-->>API: duplikáció check
    API->>DB: INSERT INTO reservations
    DB-->>API: ok
    API-->>Q: 201 + reservation JSON
    Q-->>H: invalidate cache<br/>refetch list
    H-->>FE: success state
    FE->>U: Toast: "Foglalás létrehozva"<br/>+ modal bezár
